rch engine over the wiki pages is the most obvious one — at small scale the index file is enough, but as the wiki grows you want proper search. [qmd","target":"https://github.com/tobi/qmd","line":59}],"metadata":{"title":"llm-wiki","source":"https://gist.github.com/karpathy/442a6bf555914893e9891c11519de94f","author":null,"published":null,"created":"2026-05-03","description":"llm-wiki. GitHub Gist: instantly share code, notes, and snippets.","tags":["#clippings"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"private/llm-wiki.md"},
